{
  "chapter": 144,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙箭伤初愈，与滕翼商议以伤退出狩猎以应对莫傲和管中邪的阴谋。管中邪虚伪地邀请喝酒，吕不韦召见询问遇袭之事，项少龙指出田单和旦楚为主谋。吕娘蓉闯入当面拒婚，要求选婿对象各方面胜过她，项少龙表面失望内心暗喜。入宫见小盘，小盘展现帝王气魄，以燕女和外史职位与太后做交易争取婚事自主权。昌平君为妹妹嬴盈之事道歉，透露嬴盈因被拒而发脾气。周良兄妹求见，揭示周良之妻实为其亲妹周薇，宋国亡族后裔，愿追随项少龙。太子丹来访，交付五千军马供项少龙全权调度以对付田单，双方结盟。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这两天你绝不可做激烈的动作，否则伤口爆裂，恢复期就要拖得很长了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "我想到最佳应付莫傲和管中邪阴谋的方法，是因伤退出狩猎，横竖说起打猎，我比你们差远了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那会使很多人失望。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "牧场有消息传来，清叔已依你的方法制成你提议的摺叠弩弓，可收藏于衣服内不被觉察，眼下仍须改良，要十多天时间始可大功告成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这几天很想找项大人喝酒聊天，只恨公私两忙，抽不出时间，今天出门遇贵人，相请不若偶遇，不如今晚由我请客，加上昌文君兄弟，大家欢叙一夜。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "因吕雄的事，累得管大人降官一级，我……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人勿将此等小事放在心上，吕雄是自取其咎，怨不得任何人，小弟降职是难卸罪责。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听城卫的报告，少龙昨天黄昏在城外遇袭，受了箭伤，究竟是什么一回事，知否是谁做的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "他们蒙着头脸，不过假若我没有猜错，其中一人应是田单手下的猛将旦楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "田单已识破我董马痴的身份，由于我有位好朋友落到他手上，他竟以此威胁我，幸好当时给我看穿那位朋友早给他害死，所以一时气愤下，当着他的面说要杀他报仇，他自然要先发制人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他怎能把时间拿捏得如此天衣无缝，就像我为吕雄这蠢材的事心怀不忿，派人去找你算账的模样。幸好当时我是和你一道离开，在时间上赶不及遣人吊着你和那两个刁蛮女，否则我也脱不掉嫌疑。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "当日在邯郸时，田单曾暗示在咸阳有与他勾结的人，还表示满有对付我的把握，那人当然不应是指吕相，该是昨天与会的其他六位大臣之一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "鹿公、徐先、王龁和蒙骜四人应该没有问题，余下的只有蔡泽和王绾两人，其中以蔡泽嫌疑最大，说到底他仍是因我而掉了宰相之职，哼！竟然摆出一副依附于我的模样，看我如何收拾他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "还是查清楚一点再作决定吧！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事我自有分寸，是了！娘蓉的事你决定了吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "爹不要怪守卫有疏职守，是我不准他们出声的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "text": "爹和项统领有密事商量，蓉儿怎可在外面偷听？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "只要是有关娘蓉的终身，娘蓉就有权来听。入乡随俗，秦人既有挑婿的风俗，娘蓉身为堂堂右相国之女，自应享有这权利，娘蓉有逾礼吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若想娶我吕娘蓉为妻，首先要在各方面胜得过我，才可成为我吕娘蓉的选婿对象之一。",
      "tone": "傲然",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "text": "蓉儿！",
      "tone": "不悦",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "爹！你究竟是否疼惜女儿？",
      "tone": "嗔怒",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "text": "少龙人品、剑术均无可挑剔，还说爹不疼爱你吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我并没有说一点也不喜欢他呀！只是有人更合女儿心意，除非他能证明给我看他才是更好的，否则休想女儿挑他为婿。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我的事哪到你来管，先让我看看你在田猎的表现吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "那恐怕要教小姐失望了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "text": "蓉儿不要胡闹，少龙受人暗算，伤了大腿，明天……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "连自己都保护不了，有什么资格做女儿的丈夫，爹！以后不可再提这头婚事了，女儿宁死也不会答应。",
      "tone": "不屑",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这女儿是宠坏了，少龙不须放在心上，过几天我再和她说说看。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "一切听吕相吩咐！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙是否真要杀死田单？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "想得要命，只是相当困难，当时是气愤冲口而出，事后才知太莽撞。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此事容我再想想，然后找你商议，我要先去看看李园有什么事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这都是各国精挑来送给我的美人儿，全是未经人道的上等货色，统领若有兴趣，可挑几个回去伺候你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "储君误会，我只是怕你沉迷女色，有伤身体。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "统领放心好了。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "自娘受辱惨死后，我立誓把心神全放在复仇之上，再不会把精神荒废在女人身上。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "女人有时可调剂身心，最紧要有节制。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "受教了，琴太傅常提醒我这方面的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听昌文君说你受了箭伤，去探你时师父却早睡了觉，害得我担心一晚，究竟是什么一回事？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事必有内奸，否则不会晓得两个女娃子会缠你出城比斗。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "此事交由吕不韦去烦恼吧。是了！昨天你摆明不听你母后的话，事后她有没有责怪你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她自搭上嫪毐后，就有点怕我，教训是教训了几句，还藉着我田猎的机会把管中邪升复原职，我已答应了，犯不着在这种小事上和她争拗。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "吕不韦真胆大包天，竟敢派人来和我争女人，看他日后有什么好下场。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "你欢喜鹿丹儿吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她是个相当难服侍的丫头，若论美丽，我身边的女人比得上她的大有人在，只不过非是鹿公的孙女吧！哼！我不欢喜任人安排我的婚姻，话事的人该是我这储君才对。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "我看太后是不会由你自己拿主意的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我早有应付之策。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "储君在上，微臣幸不辱命，赶了两晚夜，终弄好外史的职权，请储君过目。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_li_si",
      "text": "那个燕国美女是否仍是完璧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "微臣这两天连看她一眼的时间都找不到。",
      "tone": "尴尬",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大前天，吕不韦送了个燕女来给寡人，寡人遂转赠李卿家，哪知李卿家为了公事，竟可视美色如无物，寡人非常欣赏。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这就是寡人和太后的交易，我送她的奸夫一个大官，且附赠大屋，她自然要在寡人的婚事上做出让步。那个楚国小公主，寡人可收之为妃嫔，至于谁做储妃，则要待寡人正式加冕后再作决定。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听说项大人受了箭伤哩！现在见到你才安心点。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项卿不若由御医检视伤口好吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是我妹子不好，扯你到城外，累少龙遭人暗算。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "text": "怎可错怪令妹，这种事谁都想不到呀！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我本想找你去逛青楼，才知你受伤后提早就寝。今晚由我请客，管大人说你已答应。哼！若让我找出是谁做的，保证他人头落地。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "text": "话不要说得这么尽，敢对付我的人不会是善男信女，嘿！你的好妹子怎样了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨天由城外回来后，关上门大发脾气，又不肯吃饭，你也知我们兄弟俩公务繁忙，爹娘又早死，我们哪来这么多时间去哄她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "究竟发生什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "text": "我只是承认被打败，请她们高抬贵手再不要理会我，令妹便大发娇嗔，扯着鹿丹儿走了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看来她真的喜欢上你，嘿！你对她有意思吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "text": "自倩公主惨遭不幸后，我已心如止水，只希望专心为储君办事，再不愿有感情上的风波。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "三年前我的一名小妾因病过世，我也有你这种心情，不过男人就是男人，很快会复原过来，或者少龙需要多点的时间，只要你不是对她全无意思就成。不过我最明白嬴盈的性格，报复心重，她定会弄些事出来使你难过，唉！我也不知该怎么说了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_liang",
      "speaker_name": "周良",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小人和内人商量过，希望追随项爷办事，我家三代都是以造船为业，不知项爷有没有用得上小人的地方？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhou_liang",
      "text": "贤夫妇因何来到咸阳？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_liang",
      "speaker_name": "周良",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "实不相瞒，我们原是宋国的王族，国亡后流离失所，她……她并非小人妻子，而是小人的亲妹，为了旅途方便，才报称夫妇。今天到咸阳来是要碰碰运气，希望可以弄个户籍，干点事情，安居下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_wei",
      "speaker_name": "周薇",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小女子周薇，愿随项爷为奴为婢，只希望大哥有出头的日子。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_zi_dan",
      "speaker_name": "太子丹",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项统领果有惊人本领，李园真个要立即赶返楚国，不知统领施展什么奇谋妙计？",
      "tone": "佩服",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tai_zi_dan",
      "text": "些微小事，何足挂齿，只不知太子是否决定与项某共进退？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_zi_dan",
      "speaker_name": "太子丹",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此事我不宜出面，若我把徐夷乱的五千军马交与统领全权调度，未知统领是否觉得足够？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "尤之",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "鄙人会追随统领，以免出现调度不灵的情况。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tai_zi_dan",
      "text": "若是如此，田单休想保着项上人头。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 144,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 359
    }
  ],
